text: "Cave paintings that have been found in many parts of the earth
column4: indicate the presence of non-human beings on our planet. The following depictions are engraved in caves in the mountains of Kimberley Australia
column5: near the Prince Regent River. During a reconnaissance mission in 1838
column6: George Gray found a strange set of petroglyphs
column7: with depictions of humanoids with large eyes and oval heads
column8: figures which refer to our familiar ""greys""."
